headline: Sarah Slusser Elected to Prologis Board of Directors
summary: Prologis, Inc. (NYSE: PLD) announced today that Sarah Slusser was elected to its board of directors at the company's annual stockholder meeting on May 8, 2025. Slusser will serve on the board's Governance and Nomination committee.

headline: The Smartest Market Sell-Off Stocks to Buy With $500 Right Now
summary: One of the hardest hit sectors has been industrial REITs.  This complicated mess has led to a market sell-off and to one particular property niche of the real estate investment trust (REIT) sector getting hit extra hard.  If you like to buy the biggest and best companies in a sector, well, the standout in the industrial REIT niche is Prologis (NYSE: PLD).
